<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Weakly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Weakly,</orth> 1) without sufficient strength: <cit><quote>w. fortressed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 28" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 28</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>w. guarded,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.1.74" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 1, 74</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you are w. made,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.3.40" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 3, 40</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) indiscreetly, injudiciously, stupidly: <cit><quote>I will not adventure my discretion so w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.188" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 188</bibl></cit>.
